      <title>里夫斯希望讨好那些担心工党接管英国的银行家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/uk-election-reeves-looks-to-woo-bankers-wary-of-a-labour-uk-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新政府将不得不削减开支、提高税收或增加借贷。金融业担心这对它意味着什么。]]></description>
