      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>陪审团就特朗普封口费案进行审议。接下来会发生什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/how-could-trump-hush-money-trial-end-verdict-is-in-jurors-hands-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过六个多星期的审理，前总统唐纳德·特朗普的刑事封口费案于周二在曼哈顿下城落下帷幕。周三，胡安·默坎法官向 12 名陪审团成员指示如何将法律应用于此案——即所谓的陪审团指控——并派遣他们开始审议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/how-could-trump-hush-money-trial-end-verdict-is-in-jurors-hands-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普 2024 年竞选总统期间的法律案件时间表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-trump-trials-court-dates-legal-timeline/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普正在竞选重返白宫，同时面临多项迫在眉睫的刑事和民事审判——这是美国历史上其他候选人从未面临过的挑战。这些法律时间表有助于理解这一切]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-trump-trials-court-dates-legal-timeline/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 10:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
